      "review_summary": "The branch adds opt-in reset-family history resolution for Gateway/session tools and automatic embedded-agent carryover of one reset-archive compaction summary, with protocol/Swift/schema updates and focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +385, Tests +682, Other +4. Total +1071 across 53 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source and supplied proof rather than an independent rerun: the PR demonstrates an active reset session without a compaction summary plus ancestor reset archives containing compaction rows, then shows one carryover summary injected before the LLM boundary.",
